Package: multiROCplot
Title: Plot and Compare Multiple ROC Curves with Group Statistics
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Junjie",
           family = "Peng",
           email = "pengjunjie1996@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3532-8431"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application and supporting functions for
    exploratory diagnostic-accuracy analysis. Fits per-variable logistic
    models, overlays multiple ROC curves with areas under the curve (AUC)
    and confidence intervals, computes univariate group-comparison tests
    (t-test or Mann-Whitney) with optional false discovery rate adjustment,
    and produces annotated boxplots, with export of figures and results.
